## Advanced Theme Configuration

### Dynamic Theme Selector

```yaml
---
# Theme based on presentation type
variables:
  presentation_type: "sales"  # sales, technical, executive, training

theme: "{{presentation_type}}-theme"
# Will result in: sales-theme, technical-theme, etc.
---
```

### Conditional Themes

```yaml
---
variables:
  target_audience: "executives"
  company_tier: "enterprise"

# Conditional theme configuration
theme: |
  {% if target_audience == "executives" and company_tier == "enterprise" %}
    executive-premium
  {% elif target_audience == "executives" %}
    executive-standard
  {% elif company_tier == "enterprise" %}
    corporate-enterprise
  {% else %}
    modern-blue
  {% endif %}
---
```

