## Advanced Use Cases

### 1. **Localization and Internationalization**

```yaml
---
variables:
  locale: "en-US"
  currency: "USD"
  date_format: "MM/DD/YYYY"

  # Localized text
  texts:
    welcome: "Welcome"
    pricing: "Pricing"
    contact: "Contact"
    demo: "View Demo"

  # Localized numbers
  revenue: "$487,000"
  growth_rate: "28.5%"
  decimal_separator: "."
---

# {{texts.welcome}} to SlideLang
## Professional presentations in {{locale}}

### {{texts.pricing}}
- **Basic**: {{currency}} 29/month
- **Pro**: {{currency}} 79/month

[{{texts.demo}}](https://demo.slidelang.com/{{locale}})
```

### 2. **A/B Testing Content**

```yaml
---
variables:
  # Test version
  test_variant: "A"  # A or B

  # A/B content
  headline_a: "Boost your productivity by 300%"
  headline_b: "The tool you've been waiting for"

  cta_a: "Start Free Now"
  cta_b: "See a Personalized Demo"

  # Dynamic selection
  current_headline: |
    {% if test_variant == "A" %}{{headline_a}}{% else %}{{headline_b}}{% endif %}
  current_cta: |
    {% if test_variant == "A" %}{{cta_a}}{% else %}{{cta_b}}{% endif %}
---

# {{current_headline}}

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet...

[{{current_cta}}](https://signup.company.com?variant={{test_variant}})
```

### 3. **Environment and CI/CD Variables**

```yaml
---
# Variables injected from CI/CD
variables:
  build_number: "{{BUILD_NUMBER | default('local')}}"
  git_commit: "{{GIT_COMMIT | default('unknown')}}"
  environment: "{{ENVIRONMENT | default('development')}}"
  deploy_date: "{{DEPLOY_DATE | default('N/A')}}"

  # Dynamic URLs based on environment
  api_url: |
    {% if environment == "production" %}
      https://api.company.com
    {% elif environment == "staging" %}
      https://staging-api.company.com
    {% else %}
      http://localhost:3000
    {% endif %}
---

# API Documentation
## Environment: {{environment}} | Build: {{build_number}}

### Configuration

```javascript
const config = {
  apiUrl: '{{api_url}}',
  environment: '{{environment}}',
  version: '{{build_number}}'
};
```

*Last updated: {{deploy_date}} | Commit: {{git_commit}}*
```

