## Debugging and Troubleshooting

### Variable Verification

```yaml
---
variables:
  debug: true
  show_variables: true
---

{% if debug and show_variables %}
## Defined Variables (Debug Only)

| Variable | Value |
|----------|-------|
| guide_version | {{guide_version}} |
| last_updated | {{last_updated}} |
| author_name | {{author_name}} |
| examples_count | {{examples_count}} |
| coverage_percentage | {{coverage_percentage}} |
{% endif %}
```

### Common Errors

**1. Undefined variable:**
```yaml
# ❌ Error: variable does not exist
{{non_existent_variable}}

# ✅ Solution: default value
{{non_existent_variable | default('Default value')}}
```

**2. Incorrect YAML syntax:**
```yaml
# ❌ Error: incorrect indentation
variables:
product_name: "My Product"

# ✅ Correct: proper indentation
variables:
  product_name: "My Product"
```

**3. Special characters:**
```yaml
# ❌ Error: special characters without quotes
variables:
  description: My product: the best solution

# ✅ Correct: use quotes
variables:
  description: "My product: the best solution"
```

